summary.p:
In accordance with an embodiment of the invention, the self-propelled surface cleaning machine comprises:
a floor cleaning device;
a steerable front wheel;
a steering device associated with the front wheel;
a rear wheel device having at least one left rear wheel and at least one right rear wheel;
a first drive device for driving the front wheel;
a second drive device for driving the rear wheel device; and
a differential device for the rear wheel device that allows different speeds of rotation for the at least one left rear wheel and the at least one right rear wheel.
